    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0779a26"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000000850">真定府臨濟院</placeName><persName key="A003627">義玄</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0779a27"/><persName key="A003627">釋義玄</persName>，俗姓邢，<placeName key="PL000000022766">曹州南華</placeName>人也。參學諸方，<lb
ed="T" n="0779a28"/>不憚艱苦。因見<placeName key="PL000000019682">黃檗山</placeName><persName key="A000490">運禪師</persName>，鳴啄同時，<lb
ed="T" n="0779a29"/>了然通徹。乃北歸鄉土，俯徇趙人之請，住<pb ed="T" n="0779b" xml:id="T50.2061.0779b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0779b01"/>子城南<placeName key="PL000000000850">臨濟</placeName>焉。罷唱經論之徒，皆親堂室，<lb
ed="T" n="0779b02"/>示人心要，頗與<persName key="A003868">德山</persName>相類。以<date key="j20375112037511" when-iso="+0866-05-31">咸通七年丙<lb
ed="T" n="0779b03"/><anchor xml:id="beg0779sgsz5"/>戌<anchor xml:id="end0779sgsz5"/>歲四月十日</date>示滅。勅諡<persName key="A003627">慧照大師</persName>，塔號<lb
ed="T" n="0779b04"/>澄虛。言教頗行于世，今<placeName key="PL000000002384">恒陽</placeName>號<placeName key="PL000000000850">臨濟</placeName>禪宗<lb
ed="T" n="0779b05"/>焉。</p>
